---
title: Peruvian-Style Steaks with Bacon Fries
description: Onions, fries and steak are the perfect combination for a weeknight dinner! This dish plays on the classic Peruvian pairing, adding spicy pickled jalapeños. All together, it's guaranteed to pick you up at the end of a long day!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/steaks-a-la-peruvienne-cc268155.jpg
